        说明

        H2 Solutions Pte Ltd is a young and dynamic organisation mainly providing sales and rental of Multifunction Photocopiers and Printers in terms of hardware. Aiming to become a “One-Stop IT Solutions” company to our customers, we also specialise in Computers and Computer Peripherals, as well as other Office and Business Solutions. Founded in 2014, H2 solutions is managed by a team of very experienced staff in the IT Solutions Industry.
        H2解决方案私人有限公司是一个年轻而充满活力的组织，主要提供在硬件方面多功能复印机和打印机的销售和租赁。目标是成为一个“一站式IT解决方案”的公司给我们的客户，我们也专注于电脑及电脑周边，以及其他办公和商业解决方案。公司成立于2014年，H2的解决方案是由一个团队非常有经验的工作人员的IT解决方案行业管理。
